{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Now the-- the gendarmes-- they ordered us to roll up all the carpets, take it to some trucks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Then we had to take all the sheets and the blankets to some other trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Then we were pushed into the bedrooms, and we had to take out all the bed linen and all the leftover clothing, which they-- again, different trucks came from them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They looted-- I mean, they robbed the whole-- every flat, flat by flat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was our-- we did the job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They-- they was-- they were holding the guns and the machine guns to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they said, if anybody pockets one piece of jewelry, he would be shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Anything-- watches we have to hand always to the nearest gendarme-- gendarme just a military police-- I mean the country police.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And of course, any piece of-- any wedding rings or anything like that, if they found it in our pocket, no trial and shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "So we made sure we hand it over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And so we went from day after day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Of course, they-- every day, more and more districts were taken to the wagons, to the cattle trucks, to the cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "So we were-- we had a very busy time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We were the last strong boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "All the other people in the ghetto were either very small children, babies, or grandmothers and elderly men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was a lot of women, and right up to 95-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And then we went to kitchens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "In the kitchens, we had to-- there was a big barrel where all the honey had to go in, and a other big barrel where all the apricot jam-- we could mix the jams, actually.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Apricot jams and strawberry jams could go in the same barrel.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
